# Infrastructure ({{.Provider}})

Terraform for deploying **{{.App}}** to {{.Provider}}, scaffolded by `togo infra:init`.

```bash
# 1. Build & push the container image (see ../Dockerfile)
docker build -t {{.App}}:latest ..

# 2. Provision + deploy
togo infra:plan      # terraform plan
togo deploy          # terraform apply
```

Set provider credentials via environment/variables before applying. State stays
in this directory (or a separate infra repo) — keep it out of the app repo.
